org.antlr.intellij.adaptor.parser

Class AstBuilderListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.antlr.intellij.adaptor.parser.AstBuilderListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener

    public class AstBuilderListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This is how we build an intellij PSI parse tree (which they erroneously call an AST). We let the ANTLR parser build its kind of ParseTree and then we convert to a PSI tree in one go using a standard ANTLR ParseTreeListener.
